io.codepace.nanolog

Class Logger

  • Object
    • Logger

  • public final class Logger
extends Object
    This is a static logging class. Even though the class shouldn't be instantiated, you will have to use the init(String) method to initialize the log file.

    If init(String) isn't called before any logging occurs, a UninitializedLoggerError will be thrown
